94.title: Pact Smart Contract Language
94.description: Pact makes designing safer smart contracts effortless, whether you’re writing your first contract or launching your fiftieth dApp. It’s fundamentally different from other contract languages. It’s readable by non-developers. It automatically detects bugs, freeing you from the exploits you’ll face on Ethereum and other unsafe platforms. And it has been battle-tested in production applications for over two years.
